                <h4>Literature and/or Drama and Theory</h4>

    
              <p>12 credits in ENGL courses specific to English Literature and/or Drama and Theatre, of which at least 6 credits are at the 300 level or higher.  Please consult the complementary course lists for the English Literature and Drama and Theatre programs for course choices.</p>
    
      
      
